# Product Vision

## Problem

Most takeoff software measures walls and areas.

Estimators must still manually determine:

* Stud counts
* Plates
* Headers
* Sheathing
* Housewrap
* Connectors
* Engineered lumber
* Fasteners

This requires significant manual labor and construction knowledge.

## Solution

A-Z Takeoff automatically converts construction plans into complete material packages.

The software reads:

* Floor plans
* Elevations
* Roof plans
* Schedules
* Notes

and converts them into:

* Material quantities
* Optimized board lengths
* Package-ready bills of material

## Competitive Advantage

Existing software performs measurements.

A-Z Takeoff produces lumber-yard-ready estimates.

## Success Criteria

An experienced estimator should be able to review and finalize a generated estimate in minutes rather than hours.
